Ramsay. He's not a Miller. 
He's not from North Carolina.

35:33.764 --> 35:36.231
How does he fit in?

35:37.677 --> 35:41.025
WHEDON & MAYFIELD
INSURANCE COMPANY
46 WHITEHALL STREET
THURSDAY, SEPTEMBER 14

35:41.572 --> 35:46.008
We're here to pick up a check. 
Beau Miller? Regarding Siobhan?

35:49.547 --> 35:52.447
Mr. Miller's here to see you.

35:57.121 --> 35:59.349
Mr. Miller.

35:59.790 --> 36:04.028
My supervisor actually needs 
to handle transactions of this magnitude.

36:04.028 --> 36:06.256
Come with me.

36:07.365 --> 36:11.102
I can take your little girl 
to our day-care facility if you'd like.

36:11.102 --> 36:12.904
This won't take long, 
will it?

36:12.904 --> 36:16.974
We need to go over some delicate issues. 
It might be best.

36:16.974 --> 36:18.276
All right.

36:18.276 --> 36:20.344
Okay, now, Mommy will be back 
in just a second...

36:20.344 --> 36:22.180
and I want you to go 
with the nice lady.

36:22.180 --> 36:24.704
- Okay? 
- Okay.

36:27.885 --> 36:31.786
Mr. Mayfield? 
These are the Millers.

36:32.290 --> 36:34.892
Thank you, Tupper. 
You can go.

36:34.892 --> 36:36.928
- Welcome.
- Hello.

36:36.928 --> 36:39.430
Please, I can't tell you 
how glad I am...

36:39.430 --> 36:42.667
to be putting this unpleasant situation 
behind us.

36:42.667 --> 36:45.369
You just need to sign these.

36:45.369 --> 36:52.710
It is a detailed account 
of the event...as you relayed it to us.

36:52.710 --> 36:55.541
And we get that check today?

36:55.713 --> 36:59.113
Unless you wanna 
drop the claim.

37:08.492 --> 37:10.959
We're done in here.

37:14.131 --> 37:16.598
What is this?

37:18.236 --> 37:23.007
You're under arrest for conspiracy, 
extortion, and grand larceny.

37:23.007 --> 37:27.311
No one say anything without lawyers. 
Nothing, Siobhan.

37:27.311 --> 37:30.414
I don't understand. 
What'd I do?

37:30.414 --> 37:32.683
Why don't you tell me more 
about your dead parents?

37:32.683 --> 37:36.914
They're alive and doing time. 
Investment scams, wasn't it?

37:37.388 --> 37:40.925
I was ashamed. That's why 
I said they were dead.

37:40.925 --> 37:44.929
You ashamed of your age too? 
'Cause we know you're 23, not 17.

37:44.929 --> 37:48.193
And we know 
you participated in this.

37:49.000 --> 37:51.135
Beau made me.

37:51.135 --> 37:55.866
You don't know what they put me through. 
I didn't know what to do.

37:56.073 --> 37:59.744
- Please!
- You're good.

37:59.744 --> 38:03.179
- But I've been taken by better.
- No!

38:06.717 --> 38:09.048
I want a deal.

38:10.588 --> 38:12.857
Our cousin Kyle's job 
was to get inside.

38:12.857 --> 38:16.260
Once he was, he bumped 
a confirmed reservation and got us in.

38:16.260 --> 38:19.251
So how's Ramsay 
related to you?

38:20.264 --> 38:22.233
He's not.

38:22.233 --> 38:25.603
We found him 
on the Sex Offenders Registry.

38:25.603 --> 38:27.672
The sex was consensual. 
We set him up.

38:27.672 --> 38:31.698
And beating you to a pulp 
was what, foreplay?

38:31.776 --> 38:35.780
That was Patty Ann. 
She came in after he left.

38:35.780 --> 38:39.583
It hurt like hell, 
but she did a damn good job.

38:39.583 --> 38:40.951
I mean, 
that's pretty much it.

38:40.951 --> 38:43.788
Timed it so I got downstairs 
right in the middle of the opening...

38:43.788 --> 38:46.757
and then Kyle was in place to stop me 
just before I hit the press.

38:46.757 --> 38:49.860
Why? Wouldn't that have made 
a stronger civil suit?

38:49.860 --> 38:52.229
Oh, maybe, 
but those take years.

38:52.229 --> 38:55.599
I mean, we knew Thorpe would pay 
to keep it quiet, you know?

38:55.599 --> 38:57.335
And gag money pays real quick.

38:57.335 --> 39:00.271
You'll have to allocute to all 
of this when you plead guilty.

39:00.271 --> 39:04.900
Testify against all the other players, 
you're looking at probation.

39:06.911 --> 39:11.210
What was going through your mind when 
you were taking that beating?

39:11.716 --> 39:14.980
How I was gonna 
spend all that money.

39:16.187 --> 39:17.655
She get the deal?

39:17.655 --> 39:19.090
Yeah.
