39:19.090 --> 39:21.092
She admit to being 
the ringleader?

39:21.092 --> 39:24.695
Four separate interviews, 
one common thread: Siobhan set this up.

39:24.695 --> 39:26.764
The original scam was planned 
with the parents.

39:26.764 --> 39:28.966
Once they got pinched, 
she needed a replacement family.

39:28.966 --> 39:30.668
So she calls up 
her long-lost brother.

39:30.668 --> 39:32.036
Who, if you hear him 
tell it...

39:32.036 --> 39:34.505
had to be browbeaten 
into making the jump into the big time.

39:34.505 --> 39:35.840
And then she gets probation?

39:35.840 --> 39:37.641
I'll tell you, it gets worse:

39:37.641 --> 39:39.477
She set Ramsay up.

39:39.477 --> 39:42.480
Now, we gotta call Corrections, 
have him produced and released.

39:42.480 --> 39:44.682
I guarantee you 
he's looking at another 24 hours...

39:44.682 --> 39:46.717
before he makes it 
through the red tape.

39:46.717 --> 39:49.810
Then we need 
to put a rush on it.

39:50.065 --> 39:52.790
ALLOCUTION HEARING
FRIDAY, SEPTEMBER 15

39:52.790 --> 39:55.960
Beau made sure the police and hospital 
documented the rape...

39:55.960 --> 40:00.631
and then waited for them to arrest Ramsay 
and find out he was a convicted rapist.

40:00.631 --> 40:04.201
And, and soon as they did, 
Beau began the con.

40:04.201 --> 40:06.566
That's about it.

40:06.737 --> 40:09.440
Are the People satisfied?

40:09.440 --> 40:10.574
Miss Cabot?

40:10.574 --> 40:15.704
Could Miss Miller elaborate on how 
Russell Ramsay was enrolled in the scam?

40:16.046 --> 40:19.150
That's covered under 
the agreement, right? / Right.

40:21.085 --> 40:23.687
We just looked on the Internet 
for a sex offender.

40:23.687 --> 40:26.657
I mean, they got a whole website 
with pictures and MOs...

40:26.657 --> 40:29.593
and I picked Ramsay because 
he wasn't as gross as the others.

40:29.593 --> 40:32.129
I mean, he didn't look dangerous 
and he liked them young.

40:32.129 --> 40:34.832
How did you go about 
seducing him?

40:34.832 --> 40:36.667
Our cousin Kyle 
was the advance man.

40:36.667 --> 40:39.603
I mean, he followed him around 
a few days and got his schedule down.

40:39.603 --> 40:41.772
And then, I just showed up at his bar.

40:41.772 --> 40:44.141
I gave him the duplicate room key 
that Kyle had made...

40:44.141 --> 40:46.510
and I told him when to be in my room.

40:46.510 --> 40:51.446
The plan hinged on Ramsay showing up. 
How could you be certain he would?

40:52.116 --> 40:54.852
He's an ex-con with a loser job 
who likes young girls.

40:54.852 --> 40:56.787
I mean, it's a no-brainer.

40:56.787 --> 40:59.618
Still, something could've gone wrong.

41:00.057 --> 41:02.460
I would've Plan-B'd it.

41:02.460 --> 41:04.927
What is Plan B?

41:05.062 --> 41:09.361
Honey, no man passes up free sex.

41:11.735 --> 41:16.607
Siobhan Miller, you've entered 
a change of plea from not guilty to guilty.

41:16.607 --> 41:20.911
Are you pleading guilty because you are, 
in fact, guilty of the charges?

41:20.911 --> 41:22.179
Yes, Your Honor.

41:22.179 --> 41:24.682
Given your life-long vocation 
of flimflamming...

41:24.682 --> 41:29.119
this court is loathe to put you on the stand 
of your co-conspirators' trials.

41:29.119 --> 41:32.656
However, since your plea seems 
acceptable to the DA...

41:32.656 --> 41:35.059
this court will sentence you 
to five years probation.

41:39.263 --> 41:40.598
What are you doing?

41:40.598 --> 41:43.300
Can't tell you how much 
I've enjoyed watching you hang yourself.

41:43.300 --> 41:45.569
What? We had a deal. 
You can't go back on it.

41:45.569 --> 41:47.271
Russell Ramsay 
was attacked at Rikers.

41:47.271 --> 41:48.739
He was beaten and raped.

41:48.739 --> 41:50.474
He was killed.

41:50.474 --> 41:52.510
Your false allegation 
put him there.

41:52.510 --> 41:54.745
Under the law, 
you're responsible for his death.

41:54.745 --> 41:59.044
And manslaughter ain't covered 
under your deal, sweetheart.

42:01.652 --> 42:04.388
They got her, Munch. 
She played right into it.

42:04.388 --> 42:06.090
What are the chances it'll stick?

42:06.090 --> 42:09.193
Cabot'll get her allocution testimony 
in front of the grand jury.

42:09.193 --> 42:10.728
No way they won't indict.

42:10.728 --> 42:11.829
That's great.

42:11.829 --> 42:13.964
John. We got her.

42:13.964 --> 42:16.454
Yeah? At what price?

42:19.101 --> 42:22.112
UNIFIED SHIPPING
REGO PARK, NEW YORK
FRIDAY, SEPTEMBER 16

42:29.547 --> 42:32.917
What are you doing here? 
I thought I told you everything.

42:32.917 --> 42:34.685
I know you did. 
And you were right.

42:34.685 --> 42:36.420
What? You mean...

42:36.420 --> 42:39.256
We know that Ramsay didn't rape 
that woman. He's been cleared.

42:39.256 --> 42:41.621
Thank God.

42:46.797 --> 42:48.599
